Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,行尸走肉  前情回顾\NPreviously on AMC's The Walking Dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gabriel  - 你说你有个教堂\N- Gabriel... - You said you had a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信这家伙\NI don't trust this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他有所隐瞒\NHe's hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个储粮库  粮济全郡\NThis was the food bank. Served the whole county.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们去救Gabriel  - 怎么了？\N- We have to get Gabriel. - What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要带Eugene去华盛顿\NWe get Eugene to Washington,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以了结这一切\Nand he will make the dead die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,人类将重获世界\Nand the living will have this world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也去！就这样\NWe're in! Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息是  你还没死\NGood news is, you're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但一日将过\NBut at the end of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,人总得进食啊\Na man's got to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也许在这儿待着很蠢\NIt's probably pretty stupid to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,危机四伏\NDangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  也许不是\NI don't know, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到威胁\NYou can see the threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就那些\NThat's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看着它们会让我觉得好受点儿\NLooking at them makes me feel better about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲常说\NMy mom used to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,活一天就胜一场\Nevery day above ground was a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,太他妈有道理了  但是\NDoesn't really apply anymore, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你还可以看长远点\Nyou can still get some perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这玻璃早晚会碎\NThe glass is gonna break sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么会永垂不朽\NNothing lasts too long anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一路做标记\NYou know, we marked our way here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就能找到回去的路\Nso that we could find our way back after.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太二了  是吧？我是说…\NSo stupid, right? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,回哪儿？\Nback to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,它不仅是个陷阱\NIt wasn't just a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也是一次选择\NIt was gonna be a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:02:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我们  或被我们吃\NYou join us or feed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道\NYou know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,熊这种生物…\Nbears...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要是挨饿了\Nwhen they start to starve,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就会食子\Nthey eat their young.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要是大熊死了  幼崽还是死\NIf the bear dies, the cub dies anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果大熊活下来了\NBut if the bear lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还能再生幼崽\Nit can always have another cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,说跑偏了\NThat was part of the pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  Greg和Mike过来\NYou know, Greg and Mike came this close
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了抓那个\Nto nabbing that grey-haired queen bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我母亲的白发婊子\Nwho killed my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她和弩哥开车走了\NShe drove away with the archer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Greg看到他们扬尘而去\NGreg saw them pull away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等不及想尝尝她了\NCan't wait to try her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢女人\NI like women better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大多都是\NMost of us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟Alex曾…\NMy brother Alex has--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为Rick  他现在也不在了\Nalso currently dead because of Rick--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾说过这个理论\Nhe had a theory that it was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,女人因为生育\Nbecause of the extra layer of fat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,皮下脂肪多一层  你懂的\Nthat women have, you know, for childbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是骨感美女也是\NEven the skinny girls have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,像漂亮的…Sasha？\NLike that pretty one-- Sasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得好看的也会更好吃\NI think pretty people taste better, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会抓住他们的\NWe're going to get all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但对于初学者  你很不错了\NBut for starters, you'll do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你腿就贡献良多\NWe did a good job on your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们慢慢练\NWe've had practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦学起来  就得放慢进程了\NWhen we started, it was about making it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个人啊  在和你说话\NI'm being a human being here. I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看清形势  Bob\NPerspective, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在地上坐着\NYou're above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,至少比他们强多了\NAt least you're better off than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他疯了\NWell, he lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比我想象的疯得晚\NLasted longer than I thought he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们…\NYou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一群大傻逼\Nyou idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  放下\NOkay, keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以让他闭嘴\NI can shut him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我被咬了  你们这帮傻叉！\NI've been bitten, you stupid pricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我被感染了\NI'm tainted meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我宰了他  - 不  我们需要他\N- Let's just kill him now. - No, no, we need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可吃了丧尸肉啊\NWe might as well be eating one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那会发生什么啊？\NWhat the hell's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,会转化吗？  会死吗？\NAre we gonna turn? Are we just gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Albert  他妈冷静  我们烹饪过\NAlbert, calm the hell down. We cooked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NEverything is gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈为什么不先检查下？\NWhy the hell didn't you check him first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他好好的\N'Cause he was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 感染肉啊！ - 闭嘴\N- Tainted meat! - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们吃了丧尸肉！ - 我说了闭嘴！\N- You eating tainted meat! - I said shut up!
