Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  是我\NIt's me. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tyreese\NTyreese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他走了  - 谁？\N- He's getting away. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在监视我们\NSomebody was watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在进去\NIf we go in there now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,估计就有人出不来了\Nsome of us aren't coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob就在外面什么地方\NBob is out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕  孤独\NScared, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是独自一人\NMaybe not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryl和Carol也不见了\NDaryl and Carol are missing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对上号了\NThis is all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你一出现\NYou show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就被监视了\Nwe're being watched,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们有三个人都不见了\Nand now three of us are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我没…\NI don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟这事没一点关系\NI don't have anything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等！ - 别！\N- Wait! - Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sasha  收起来  - 谁在外面？\N- Sasha, put it away. - Who's out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我跟这…\NI-- I don't have anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有一点关系  - 我们的人呢？\N- to do with this. - Where are our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我跟这事没  - 我们的人呢？\N- I don't have anything to-- - Where are our people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  我跟这事没一点关系\NPlease, I don't have anything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\NI--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么把我们带到这？\NWhy'd you bring us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  我…\NPlease, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟谁一起工作？\NYou working with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人  我自己\NI'm alone. I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直一个人\NI was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个储粮库的女人呢  Gabriel？\NWhat about the woman in the food bank, Gabriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你对她做了什么？\NWhat did you do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“你会被这一切焚尽”\N"You'll burn for this."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是你写的吧  为什么？\NThat was for you. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为了什么被焚啊  Gabriel？\NWhat are you gonna burn for, Gabriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说？  你做了什么？\NWhat? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你过去做了什么？！\NWhat did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚上把门关上了\NI lock the doors at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常晚上把门关上的\NI always lock the doors at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常晚上把门关上的\NI always lock the doors at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常…\NI always--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们陆续过来  我的子民们\NThey started coming, my congregation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,之前亚特兰大在晚上被轰炸了\NAtlanta was bombed the night before
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们害怕了\Nand they were scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们…他们在寻找一个安全的地方\NThey were-- they were looking for a safe place,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一个他们觉得安全的地方\Na place where they felt safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那会儿还早  很早\NAnd it was so early. It was so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以门还关着\NAnd the doors were still locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你看…\NYou see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的选择\Nit was my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们人太多了\NThere were so many of them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们试图撬开百叶窗\Nand they were trying to pry the shutters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,使劲撞击侧面  冲我叫唤\Nand banging on the sidings, screaming at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那些行尸就向他们去了\NAnd so the dead came for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,妇人…\NWomen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子\Nchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人痛苦的喊着我的名字\NEntire families calling my name as they were torn apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请求我的怜悯\Nbegging me for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请求我的怜悯\NBegging me for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我该下地狱啊\NDamning me to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我焚烧了他们的尸骨\NI buried their bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都烧了\NI buried it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,主最终还是让你来惩罚我了\NThe Lord sent you here to finally punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我该死\NI'm damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前该死\NI was damned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常锁着门\NI always lock the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,锁着门\NI always lock the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿有…\NThere's something--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,玻璃外有人躲着\Nthere's someone outside lying in the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha\NSasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob！\NOh! Bob!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob\NBob.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他的腿  - 把Bob带进去\NHis leg. - Get Bob inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会照顾好他们的\NWe'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮帮我吗  求你了？\NCan you help me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我  帮帮我\NHelp me. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,进去！\NGet inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快去！\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前在墓地\NI was in the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把我打晕了\NSomebody knocked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚醒来就在这里了\NI woke up outside this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那看起来像个学校\NIt looked like a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个人  Gareth\NIt was that guy, Gareth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他5个人\NAnd five other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在我面前吃我的腿\NThey were eating my leg right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这没什么一样\NLike it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就像无比自豪的了结了一切\NAll proud like they had it all figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她们抓了Daryl和Carol吗？\NDid they have Daryl and Carol?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gareth说他们开车走了\NGareth said they drove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他很痛  有什么能用的？\NHe's in pain. Do we have anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得急救箱里应该有药品\NI think there are pill packets in the first aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恩  - 留着吧\N- Yeah. - Save 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  - 说真的\N- No. - Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我在储粮库时被咬了\NIt happened at the food bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob\NBob?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我办公室里有个沙发\NThere's a sofa in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这不算什么  但…\NI know it's not much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我来吧\NI got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道Bob说的那个地方吗？\NDo you know the place Bob was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是个小学\NIt's an elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 离这儿很近  - 多近？\N- It's close. - How close?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,多近啊  Gabriel？\NHow close, Gabriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从这走十分钟  穿过树林就到了\NIt's just a 10-minute walk through the woods from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在墓地的正南方\Ndue south of the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\NShh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他是发烧了吗？\NDoes he have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有点热\NHe's just warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim大概活了两天\NJim lasted almost two days
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们就丢下他了\Nbefore we left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,该面对现实了\NTime for a reality check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在全部都要去特区\NWe all need to leave for DC right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryl和Carol会回来的\NDaryl and Carol are gonna be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没有他们我们哪儿都不去\NWe're not going anywhere without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我赞赏你的态度\NI respect that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但明显现在Eugene有危险\Nbut there's a clear threat here to Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我得保护好他  防止事态恶化\NI need to extract his ass before things get any uglier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们不愿意来  祝你们好运\NSo if y'all won't come, good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们做你们的  我做我的\NWe'll go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你就打算步行吗？\NYou leaving on foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把那辆车修好了\NWe fixed that damn bus ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这儿的人还有那么多\NThere are a lot more of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你就想一直这样吗？你来啊\NYou want to keep it that way? You should come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Carol救了你的命  我们救了你的命\NCarol saved your life. We saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而我是在救你们大家命\NWell, I am trying to save yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,救每个人的\NSave everyone's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不会分头行动的\NWe're not going anywhere without our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们的人都逃了  - 他们会回来的\N- Your people took off. - They're coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,回来干啥？来看你们剩下的骨头吗？\NTo what, picked-over bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还没明白  - 别碰我！\N- You're not taking - Do not lay hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Abraham！- 喂  打住！打住！\N- Abraham! - Hey, hey, stop! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得  你大半夜的这样离开\NDo you really think that you're gonna be any safer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会更安全吗？\Nleaving right now in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天呢？\NWhat about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要团结才能做到\NWe need each other for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要团结才能到达特区\NWe need each other to get to DC.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们团结就可以渡过这一切\NWe can get through all of it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个想法\NI have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你多待一天帮助我们\NIf you stay just one more day and help,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你们去特区  不论发生什么\NI'll go with you to DC no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Glenn和Maggie也来\NGlenn and Maggie, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行  - 那祝你们好运\N- No. - Good luck, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你们的人也不感兴趣\NI'm not interested in breaking up what you have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosita 抄起你的家伙\NRosita, grab your gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Abraham  - 少废话！\N- Abraham - Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Euegne  我们走  Euegne\NEugene, let's go. Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,起来\NMove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想  - 快起来！\N- I don't want to. - Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能用那辆公车\NYou're not taking the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,试着拦下我啊！\NTry to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着  慢着\NWait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 喂\NHey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你留下来\NYou stay--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,留下来帮助我们\Nyou stay and help us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就跟你走\Nand we will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  - 这不是你说了算\N- No. - It's not your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你留下来帮我们\NYou stay, help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就半天\NHalf a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正午走  时间紧迫\NCome high noon, we're taillights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再多等了\NI'm not waiting for the other damn shoe to drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会和你走的\NAnd we will leave with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,12个小时\N12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就走\NThen we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其实  我脸上被打\NYou know, the one good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个好处\Nabout getting kicked in my face--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是让我忘了腿上的疼痛\Nmade me forget the pain in my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我半身的疼痛  所以是两个好处\NAnd my side, so two good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别再说傻话了\NWe're not playing that game anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,恩…\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,从各面考虑\Nall things considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可以逗我笑一下\Nfigured you could humor me a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被咬后\NWhy didn't you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我？\Nwhen it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI knew
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你的话\Nwhen I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就会像一切都结束了\Nit'd become all about the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而我很享受这个过程\NAnd I really liked the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以为他们掌控了局面\NThey think they're in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在明  他们在暗\NWe're in here and they could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们知道他们的确切位置\NBut we know exactly where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,计划受阻  我只能这么说\NPlan's got stones, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们得赶在他们前面　- 没错\N- Make our move before they do. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不指望我们头脑清晰\NThey're not counting on us thinking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗？\NAre we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想确认一下　这可不是件小事\NI'm just making sure. It's a big play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,时刻记得提防这些人\NRemember what these people are capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tyreese  - 怎么了？\N- Tyreese. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗？\NYou up for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你们一起去\NI'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该和Bob呆一块儿\NYou should stay with Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不　我想出去\NNo, I want to be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想参与进来\NI want to be a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这是什么感觉\NI know how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在这里\NBut this right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和他在一起\Nthe time you could have with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能错过这个机会\Nyou can't throw that away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我和Karen有这样的机会\NI wish I had it with Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得当时的感受吗？\NDo you remember how you felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你当时想做的事？\NWhat you wanted to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那让我迷茫\NIt made it so I couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,饶恕\NForgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢面对\NThat's facing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该饶恕他们吗？\NI should forgive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:30:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs1\t(0,150,\fs4\frz90)\t(150,300,\fs7\frz180)\t(300,450,\fs10\frz270)\t(450,600,\fs13\frz360)\t(600,750,\fs16\frz450)\t(750,900,\fs19\frz540)\t(900,1050,\fs22\frz630)\t(1050,1200,\fs25\frz720)\fad(0,1000)\pos(602,66)\org(555,105)\c&H0000FF&\fn华文行楷}真爱字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算伤害他  想要杀了我们？\NFor hurting him? For trying to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了？\NWhat the hell is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们还有选择吗？\NYou think we have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是所有的人都能选择\NNot all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你有\NJust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他睁开眼\NWhen he opens his eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一想看到的就是你的脸\Nthe only thing he's gonna want to see is your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着\NTake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果他停止呼吸…　　- Sasha\N- If he stops breathing... - Sasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…你把这个穿过他的太阳穴\N...you put it through his temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Bob想要的\NThat's what Bob would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你知道我们在这\NWell, I guess you know we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也知道你们在这\NAnd we know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们武器齐全\NAnd we're armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所有没必要躲躲藏藏了\NSo there's really no point in hiding anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.13,0:24:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在监视你们\NWe've been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.11,0:24:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道都有谁在\NWe know who's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob在\NThere's Bob,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.73,0:24:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们还没结束他的痛苦\Nunless you've put him out of his misery already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.29,0:24:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有Eugene\NAnd Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.16,0:25:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosita\NRosita.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.38,0:25:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin的好朋友Tyreese\NMartin's good friend Tyreese.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.42,0:25:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl\NCarl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.92,0:25:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Judith\NJudith.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick和其他人出去了\NRick and the rest walked out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.81,0:25:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着你们大部分枪\Nwith a lot of your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.19,0:25:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,听着　我们不知道你们在哪里\NListen, we don't know where you all are,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.99,0:25:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个地方不大\Nbut this isn't a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.83,0:25:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在别闹了\NSo let's just stop this now
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.62,0:25:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别把事情搞得更糟糕\Nbefore things get more painful than they need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.53,0:26:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,听着　你们就躲在某一扇门后\NLook, you're behind one of these two doors
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.48,0:26:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们手上武器干掉你们\Nand we have more than enough firepower
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.04,0:26:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是绰绰有余\Nto take down both.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.82,0:26:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该不是你们想要的吧\NCan't imagine that's what you all want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.74,0:26:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个神父怎么样？\NHow about the priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.13,0:26:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,神父　你帮我们把事办好\NFather, you help us wrap this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就让你走\Nwe'll let you walk away from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.58,0:26:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要把门打开　你就可以走了\NJust open the door and you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.15,0:26:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把小婴儿带走\NYou can take the baby with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.15,0:26:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样？\NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以留下这个孩子\NI don't know. Maybe we'll keep the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.70,0:27:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我越来越喜欢这小女孩了\NI'm starting to like this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.95,0:27:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你最后的机会了　\NIt's your last chance right now
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.08,0:27:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,马上出来\Nto tell us you're coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.96,0:27:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,完了吗？\NAre we done?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放在地板上\NPut your guns on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.13,0:27:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick　我们直接朝那间办公室开枪　\NRick, we'll fire right into that office.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.78,0:27:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你把枪拿低点\NSo you lower your gun--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.34,0:27:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放地上　跪下\NPut your guns on the floor and kneel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.68,0:27:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,照他说的做\NDo what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.16,0:28:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin　我们没有其他选择了\NMartin, there's no choice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.66,0:28:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不　我们还有选择\NYeah, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.67,0:28:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想打个赌吗？\NWant to bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.40,0:28:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,求饶也没有意义了　对吧？\NNo point in begging, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.04,0:28:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.16,0:28:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你进来的时候　有机会杀掉我们的\NStill, you could have killed us when you came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.96,0:28:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NThere had to be a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.16,0:28:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想浪费子弹\NWe didn't want to waste the bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.27,0:29:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们以前帮过人\NWe used to help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.17,0:29:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拯救别人\NWe saved people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.59,0:29:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在变了　他们来了　\NThings changed. They came in and--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.27,0:29:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后\NAfter that...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.70,0:29:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在外面呆过　但我也知道\NI know that you've been out there, but I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.53,0:29:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道饥肠辘辘是何感受\NYou don't know what it is to be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.93,0:29:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必这样做\NYou don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.43,0:29:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以走得远远的\NWe can walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.10,0:29:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们永无交集\NAnd we will never cross paths again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.05,0:29:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓\NI promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.30,0:29:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但你会遇上其他的人\NBut you'll cross someone's path.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.14,0:30:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,会对其他人做同样的事\NYou'd do this to anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.03,0:30:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧？\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.36,0:30:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而且\NBesides,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.62,0:30:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经给过你承诺了\NI already made you a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.07,0:30:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.19,0:31:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能本是我们的下场\NIt could have been us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.11,0:31:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.92,0:31:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可是教堂啊\NThis is the Lord's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.59,0:31:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.26,0:32:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这仅仅是一个顶盖四面墙\NIt's just four walls and a roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.11,0:32:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远与我们同在\NYou'll always be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.63,0:32:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的一员\NPart of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.52,0:32:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick.\NRick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.19,0:32:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不必\NNo, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.66,0:32:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就抱着她吧\NLet her stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.87,0:32:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她会乖的\NI trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.42,0:32:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在门外\NI'm right outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.05,0:32:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想对你说声谢谢\NI just want to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.22,0:32:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.85,0:32:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在我到监狱之前\NBefore the prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.22,0:32:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直不知道世上还有没有好人了\NI didn't know if there were any good people left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.69,0:33:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道是否还有人活着\NI didn't know if anybody was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.40,0:33:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但你加我入伙\NYou took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.60,0:33:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是你把人们都凝聚起来了\N'Cause you took people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.08,0:33:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是你  伙计\NIt was you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.30,0:33:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天所说的\NWhat I said yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.67,0:33:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不会改口\NI ain't revising it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.81,0:33:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是现在这种世道\NEven in light of current events.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.06,0:33:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噩梦过后\NNightmares end.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.27,0:33:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不会在噩梦中迷失自己\NThey shouldn't end who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.24,0:33:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我这个将死之人想要说的\NAnd that is just this dead man's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.75,0:34:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我会记在心里的\NI'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.04,0:34:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看看她\NJust look at her
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.13,0:34:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像这个世界未曾改变\Nand tell me the world isn't gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.37,0:34:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不行了\NYou were out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.16,0:34:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.87,0:34:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NWas I?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.71,0:34:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYou were.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.63,0:34:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么在笑？\NWhy are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.54,0:34:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像正在做梦\NI think I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.90,0:34:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且梦见你\NAnd I think you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.91,0:35:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对我灿烂地笑着\Nwere smiling back at me in the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.45,0:35:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对  就像这样\NYeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.91,0:35:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那这算什么？\NSo what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.53,0:35:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是因祸得福吗？\NThe good that comes out of this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.64,0:35:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob?\NBob?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.02,0:35:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob?\NBob?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.76,0:36:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来吧\NGive it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.86,0:36:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你在外面等着\NYou step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.50,0:36:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.22,0:37:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们去特区的路线图\NThis is our route to DC.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.39,0:37:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们沿着这个一直走\NWe'll stick to it as long as we're able.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.18,0:37:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不行  你们也知道我们在哪\NIf not, well, you got our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.68,0:37:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只要Eugene拿到了解药\NOnce Eugene gets to the big brains left up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.73,0:37:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,世界就会复原了\Nthings are gonna bounce back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这支队伍应该为此而去\NThis group should be there for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.86,0:38:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你应为此前行\NYou should be there for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.59,0:38:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会的\NThey will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.10,0:38:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会的\NWe will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.20,0:38:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们会\NWe will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.29,0:38:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.29,0:39:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\\fn华文新魏\pos(429,56)\c&HFFFFFF&}华盛顿特区
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.49,0:39:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\c&HFFFFFF&\\fn华文新魏\pos(342,71)}对不起  我混球  来华盛顿吧\N新的世界需要Rick Grimes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.35,0:39:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不知道对于你来说\NI never asked how it was for you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.81,0:39:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,终点站意味着什么\Ngetting to Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.45,0:40:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,会杀了我\NIt killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.01,0:40:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不  它不会\NNo, it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.53,0:40:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡不着\NI can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.55,0:41:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  坐在这里\NAnd now, sitting in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.43,0:41:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一片寂静\NQuiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.73,0:41:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不像昨晚一样\NIt isn't just what happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.73,0:41:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,整夜回荡着当时凄惨声音\NSaying what happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.04,0:41:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,震耳响亮\Nout loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.07,0:41:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我能回想那个场景\NI see it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.08,0:41:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那惨叫仿佛就在耳边\NI hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.88,0:41:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.41,0:42:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs1\t(0,150,\fs4\frz90)\t(150,300,\fs7\frz180)\t(300,450,\fs10\frz270)\t(450,600,\fs13\frz360)\t(600,750,\fs16\frz450)\t(750,900,\fs19\frz540)\t(900,1050,\fs22\frz630)\t(1050,1200,\fs25\frz720)\fad(0,1000)\pos(602,66)\org(555,105)\c&H0000FF&\fn华文行楷}真爱字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.50,0:41:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它不会停止\NThat won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.84,0:41:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但总不会一直这样\NBut it won't be all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.97,0:42:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Carol去哪了？\NWhere's Carol?
